    Возраст: &lt;input type="text" name="age" /&gt;
&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Пол:
&lt;input id="female" type="radio" 
name="gender" value="f"&gt;
&lt;label for="female"&gt;Женский&lt;/label&gt;
&lt;input id="male" type="radio" 
name="gender" value="m"&gt;
